msgid "The Active checkbox controls whether the account can sign in at all. Regular User is the fallback viewer role only and is removed automatically when Writer, Approver, Manager, or elevated internal roles are assigned. Internal User is an add-on viewer role and can be combined with Regular User. Custom non-role groups can still be used later for notifications or department grouping."
